471
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:22,230
Dejima-san, chcela by si sa ku mne pridať?

472
00:20:22,230 --> 00:20:22,980
Prepáčte?

473
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:26,730
Prečo si mi dievčatá občas nedoprajeme trochu nahoty?

474
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,480
Doprajeme nahoty?

475
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:31,740
Tak teda prijmem vašu ponuku.

476
00:20:34,780 --> 00:20:36,620
