477
00:20:36,620 --> 00:20:38,520
To bolí!

478
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:40,650
Udrel som si ruku o roh lavice.

479
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:43,370
T-Tsuda!

480
00:20:43,980 --> 00:20:45,830
Tvoja pravá ruka môže byť tvojou milenkou,

481
00:20:45,830 --> 00:20:47,900
